(145, 1, '2018-03-20 10:05:32', '2018-03-20 14:05:32', '<style>.entry-header {display: none;}</style>\r\n<h1 style=\"font-size: 2.75rem; font-family: Montserrat, \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;     font-weight: 700;\r\n    line-height: 1.25;\"><center><strong>Subscription Policy</strong></center></h1>\r\n“Through the Eyes” is an E Magazine that enlightens its readers to the different views of authors that share the interest with Cinemalaya Film Festival. In line with this, the subject of each article consists of their different perspectives through their eyes as an audience, a director or an actor. This is used only as a medium to further understand and digest the highlighted socially relevant films. Furthermore, the contents of this material shall; willingly share to its readers and be used as a guide to future researchers or enthusiasts but only when the author is acknowledged., not encourage any plagiarism of any kind so as to respect the author\'s personal insights and views on any particular matter, and, maintain professionalism by refraining from libellous or otherwise unlawful, abusive or obscene material.\r\n\r\nFor the benefit of the subscriber, any information needed will not be released to the public or any third party without permission from the user or as required by law. It will remain private so as to respect the individual\'s human right of privacy. The subscriber will also acquire his/her animosity to be able to freely accept it\'s requests and comments to further improve the future E-magazines that will be published.', 'Subscription Policy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'subscription-policy', '', '', '2018-03-20 10:07:54', '2018-03-20 14:07:54', '', 0, 'http://throughtheeyes.info/iteration1/?page_id=145', 0, 'page', '', 0),
